# Input

```scss
.foo {
  @include transition(min-height ($spacer/2) ease-in-out);
}
// Biome intentionally normalizes slash binary expressions to operator spacing.
.bar {
  @include transition(min-height, $spacer/2, ease-in-out);
}

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,7 +1,7 @@
 .foo {
-  @include transition(min-height ($spacer/2) ease-in-out);
+  @include transition(min-height ($spacer / 2) ease-in-out);
 }
-
+// Biome intentionally normalizes slash binary expressions to operator spacing.
 .bar {
-  @include transition(min-height, $spacer/2, ease-in-out);
+  @include transition(min-height, $spacer / 2, ease-in-out);
 }
```

# Output

```scss
.foo {
  @include transition(min-height ($spacer / 2) ease-in-out);
}
// Biome intentionally normalizes slash binary expressions to operator spacing.
.bar {
  @include transition(min-height, $spacer / 2, ease-in-out);
}
```
